name: Trava Capital
public_notice: The smart-contract owner can mint new tokens, please proceed with caution.

description.en: Trava Capital is a Venture Capital. Utilizing the Treasury from the previous system, Trava Capital continues growing the Treasury and invests in on-chain assets and on-chain services. Moreover, Trava Capital allows its users to pool their capital and invest in various projects. The DAO shall determine the investment decisions.
